Package: gnafr
Type: Package
Title: Australian Address Matching Using GNAF
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kyle", "Haynes", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "kyle@kylehaynes.com.au")
Description: Fast bulk address matching against the Geocoded National Address
    File (GNAF) for Australia. Supports fuzzy matching with a confidence
    scoring algorithm, DuckDB-backed storage for high-performance lookups
    (100k+ addresses), and the ability to add custom addresses to the
    matching database.
